The paper discusses the development of natural language interfaces that generate visual interpretations, which involves both artificial intelligence and visualization aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
